/apps/2535600/extras/9af560abebc96b0248dc9d0316db1198.webp?t=1725944212\" width=616 height=7 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535600/extras/09e5f227bcced48708da1c7acbd4f29f.poster.avif?t=1725944212\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535600/extras/09e5f227bcced48708da1c7acbd4f29f.webm?t=1725944212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535600/extras/09e5f227bcced48708da1c7acbd4f29f.mp4?t=1725944212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><u>COSMIC COUNTDOWN</u></strong><br>Time waits for no one in the void of space. With every tick of the speedrun timer, the pressure mounts. Can you master the course and beat the clock? Optional checkpoints are there to help, but the true test is how fast you can reach the end without them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535600/extras/9af560abebc96b0248dc9d0316db1198.webp?t=1725944212\" width=616 height=7 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535600/extras/69794de6e196bb6524469cad40bf09de.poster.avif?t=1725944212\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535600/extras/69794de6e196bb6524469cad40bf09de.webm?t=1725944212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535600/extras/69794de6e196bb6524469cad40bf09de.mp4?t=1725944212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><u>ONE MORE JUMP</u></strong><br>It’s all or nothing. One wrong move sends you back to the start. Precision controls and mastering razor-sharp movement are your only allies in this space odyssey.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535600/extras/9af560abebc96b0248dc9d0316db1198.webp?t=1725944212\" width=616 height=7 /></span>",
